      • updateWith

        public boolean updateWith(TrackedElement tp)
        Update with an external element. This is used for tracking purposes. The current element is updated with the data of the new one passed in parameter. the new one is to be deleted afterwards.
        Parameters:
        tp -
        Returns:

      • updateAlone

        public void updateAlone()
        Update the element without an external one. This is called when no good candidate is found. The filtering may set a new position and speed.
